        <p><strong>Note:</strong> India, Pakistan, and several other countries with large UAE expat populations are NOT Hague members. Documents from these countries require full embassy legalization chain.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Documents Commonly Apostilled</h2>

      <div class="document-grid">
        <div class="doc-item">
          <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
          <span>Birth Certificates</span>
        </div>
